In the golang_learn folder,

How to run files.go?
% go run base/usages/files/files.go ./base/usages
% go run base/usages/files/files.go ./base

how to run read_file_defer.go?
go run base/usages/files/read_file_defer.go base/usages/files/data.txt

how to run read_file.go?
% go run base/usages/files/read_file.go
